      "title": "BREAKING: Sri Lankan President\u2019s House stormed by protestors",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lankan protestors have taken control of the President\u2019s House located in Fort, Colombo. Thousands of ordinary Sri Lankans marched to the President\u2019s House demanding the immediate resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa."
